{[#]Black is slightly underdeveloped and the kingside pin is unpleasant. My
opponent hoped somewhat freing his position with} 12... h6 {Ho would you
proceed?} 13. Bh4 $1 $16 ({This pseudo-sacrifice ensures weakening the
kingside structure with Ne4.} 13. Bxf6 Qxf6 {is also more pleasant for White,
but Black would have no immediate worries.}) 13... g5 $2 {The remedy is worse
than the initial problem.} 14. Nxg5 hxg5 15. Bxg5 {There is no adequate
defense against Ne4.} Ne5 16. Qh4 Ng6 17. Bxf6 Nxh4 18. Bxe7 Nxg2 19. Bxf8 Ne3
20. fxe3 Bxe3+ 21. Kg2 Kxf8 22. Rf3 Bc5 23. Raf1 f5 24. e4 Bd7 25. exf5 exf5
26. Rxf5+ 1-0

