Nf6 19. Rfb1 Qc3 20. e3 $14 Rd8 (20... Nd5 21. Qf3 $14) 21. g4 $36) 13... c3 (
13... cxb3 14. Nd3 $18) (13... f6 14. Nexc4 Nxc4 15. bxc4 $16) 14. Ndc4 {
The signal to the attack.} Nxc4 (14... c2+ 15. Qd2 Qxd2+ 16. Kxd2 Nxc4+ 17.
bxc4 $16) (14... O-O $2 15. Nd3 Qxb3 16. Nxd6 $18) 15. Qxf7+ Kd8 16. Nxc4 c2+ (
16... Qxb3 17. Qxg7 $18) 17. Nd2 Qxd4 18. Rc1 Na6 19. Qf4 $5 ({This is the
